 <h4>Answer the following questions to write a paragraph on ‘Healthy Food’. You should write it in about 250 words ᐅ</h4>
 <br><br>
 <h3><center>Healthy Food</center></h3>
 
 <p>Food is something that we eat . It is essential for our body for a number of reasons. It provides us with the energy needed for working, playing, and doing day-to-day activities. It helps us to grow, makes our bones and muscles strong, repairs damaged body cells, and boosts our immunity against external harmful elements.
 
 Healthy food refers to foods that contain beneficial nutrients.It nourishes both our physical and mental health and helps us stay active for many years. Healthy diet is essential for good health and nutrition. It protects us from many disease heart disease, diabetes and cancer. Eating a variety of foods and consuming less salt, sugars are essential for healthy diet. Healthy food provides us with many important nutrients including carbohydrates, protein, fat, minerals, vitamins, and water. Healthy food produces energy for our body and runs all the functions of the body smoothly. It also keeps our immune system healthy.
 
 In conclusion we can say that healthy food is necessary to keep our body fit and mind fresh. It is necessary to eat a healthy and balanced diet. Doing so will help us to become fit both physically and mentally.</p>
